WEBVTT

33:00.214 --> 33:02.923
It's not right.
Look at him, he needs freedom.

33:03.506 --> 33:04.923
Let's not treat him like an animal.

33:05.214 --> 33:06.089
Untie the rope.

33:06.298 --> 33:08.089
What if he escapes?
-He won't.

33:08.506 --> 33:09.381
Untie him.

33:12.089 --> 33:14.881
Hey, Boka. What did you like here?

33:17.131 --> 33:18.464
[tribal language]

33:22.298 --> 33:22.923
Pua!

33:23.381 --> 33:24.298
What is Pua?

33:30.256 --> 33:32.048
Don't touch me.
Are you mad?
